_json.description: Free Printable Cottage Style Mason Jar Tags These Free Printable Cottage Style Mason Jar Tags are perfect to hang on gifts and especially fabulous for hanging on Mason Jars filled with preserves… pickled vegetables… jams and more! Spring is coming and many of you will be whipping up some fabulous Jams and Preserves… you will also be making yummy treats for Easter and much much more! So… having some pretty Tags to put on these delicious creations would probably be very helpful…
